Revision history for IO-Pty-HalfDuplex

0.02    Wed Jun 17 19:17:41 PDT 2009
        Fixed a bug which would cause a crash on kill() calls
        Added ptrace and sysctl backends for high performance on BSD
        Added multi-backend support; see documentation for details
        Wrote a blog post documenting the problem, commited to doc/
        Removed a darcs backup file from packaging (oops)
        Fixed Changes date for 0.01

0.01    Tue Jun  9 18:36:15 PDT 2009
        First version, released on an unsuspecting world.

